title: Tottenham Tiptoe Into Round of 16
description:
The FC crew discuss Tottenham's narrow win over Marseille to advance into the UCL Round of 16 but question whether Antonio Conte's tactics will work going forward. Plus, Liverpool end Napoli's undefeated start to the season and Atletico Madrid's European competition elimination puts Diego Simeone under serious pressure.
